- Added `LINT_PRESETS` array and `buildLintConfigFromPreset()` helper to `lintRules.ts`; three presets: Strict (all rules, error severity, tight thresholds), Recommended (color/alias/duplicate rules, warning severity), Permissive (alias depth only, info severity)
